desc_long								关于这款游戏							Call in sick and unplug the phone! The third installment of the award-winning Mahjong series lets you choose from three different play modes, create tile sets and backdrops, make layouts to share, and chat with players using in-game messaging. The enthralling fun of Mahjong is something that everyone in the family can enjoy!										More than 40,000 layouts.					Chat with other players.					Create and share custom boards.																
